<L>__{exterior pi's primary school, 1972 day}
<A>__{pi (age 11) leans against the railing of a balcony, reading "l'ile mysterieuse (the mysterious island)" by jules verne.}
<C>__{adult pi }
<D>__{imagine me trying to explain that name to my schoolmates. i barely made it to the age of eleven before...}
<A>__{a boy (bully #1) calls up to him from the courtyard below.}
<D>__{bully #1 hey piscine!}
<A>__{pi glances down, all the boys in the courtyard watching him.}
<P>__{bully #1 (cont'd)}
<D>__{are you pissing right now?}
<A>__{pi freezes. the other boys laugh uncontrollably.}
<C>__{another boy}
<D>__{look at him he's pissing!}
<C>__{adult pi }
<D>__{with one word my name went from an elegant french swimming pool to a stinking indian latrine. i was pissing everywhere.}
<A>__{i e. schoolyard, 1972 day boys in school uniform kick a ball. pi attempts to join. bully #2 intercepts the pass.}
<D>__{bully #2 no pissing in the schoolyard!}
